{"tid":1043461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生斥副校長奶共「屎忽鬼」誹謗入罪  理大判決書曝光","createTime":"2019-03-02T09:40:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T12:41:54.000Z","uid":45148,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6b1b1648427cbab84213cce75f873b44f92331","tid":1043461,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T09:40:08.000Z","msg":"理工大學去年爆發「連儂牆」風波，多名學生代表因闖入大學高層辦公室要求對話引致衝突，其中4人分別被處罰停學、社會服務令及即時退學兼永不取錄。理大學生紀律委員會指控涉事學生4項罪名，包括出言譴責時任暫任副校長（學生）沈岐平和學務長莫志明，「你哋收共產黨錢收得咁過癮，舐共舐得你哋咁開心呀啦，屎忽鬼」，被指誹謗成立。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/173317_d96324100d0ea7a50bee068e8454352f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F173317_d96324100d0ea7a50bee068e8454352f.jpg&h=eb2a9a73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖中為被理大學生誹謗為&ldquo;屎忽鬼&rdquo;既沈岐平副校長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/173424_3a342d5e45373b12c48af785f3c9b1c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F173424_3a342d5e45373b12c48af785f3c9b1c2.jpg&h=7e15997e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖中為另一位被誹謗為&ldquo;屎忽鬼&rdquo;既學務長莫志明先生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔應該叫理大師長為屎忽鬼<br />\n屎忽鬼稱呼對師長十分不尊重<br />\n<br />\n在此向誹謗副校長為屎忽鬼既學生深表不滿</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190302&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59321626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190302%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59321626&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWsIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=f790918b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190302%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59321626&h=3f551129\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190302&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59321626</a>"},{"pid":"963522cf14f053f2c6a59a092baf4414f32f5daf","tid":1043461,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T09:41:25.000Z","msg":"舉頭望明月，低頭屎忽鬼。"},{"pid":"9e8b5d9d856ba6d155db5b56ac957ed23263730f","tid":1043461,"uid":147079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}